# GMAIL

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User ig.paraskun@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass google/paraskun/mutt/pass"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail-general
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel gmail-sent
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Near :gmail-local:Sent
Create Near
Expunge Both

Channel gmail-trash
Far :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Near :gmail-local:Trash
Create Near
Expunge Both

Group gmail
Channel gmail-general
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-trash

# NSTU

IMAPAccount nstu
Host mail2.nstu.ru
User "paraskun.2022@stud.nstu.ru"
PassCmd "pass nstu/pass"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore nstu-remote
Account nstu

MaildirStore nstu-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/nstu/
Inbox ~/.mail/nstu/Inbox

Channel nstu-general
Far :nstu-remote:
Near :nstu-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both

Channel nstu-sent
Far :nstu-remote:"Sent"
Near :nstu-local:Sent
Create Near
Expunge Both

Channel nstu-trash
Far :nstu-remote:"Trash"
Near :nstu-local:Trash
Create Near
Expunge Both

Group nstu
Channel nstu-general
Channel nstu-sent
Channel nstu-trash
